import React, { Component } from 'react'; import './Business.css'; const business = { imageSrc: 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/codecademy-content/programs/react/ravenous/pizza.jpg', name: 'MarginOtto Pizzeria', address: '1010 Paddington Way', city: 'Flavortown', state: 'NY', zipCode: '10101', category: 'Italian', rating: 4.5, reviewCount: 90 } class Business extends React.Component{ render(){ return(

{business.name}

{business.address}

{business.city}

{business.state} {business.zipCode}

{business.category}

{business.rating}

{business.reviewCount}

) } } export default Business;
